      "side": 1,
      "message": "not pretty, but you can do:\n\n`$ vpython3 -vpython-spec run_tests.vpython3 -m black ...`\n\nwhich is why i have a local script:\n\n```\n$ cat run_black\n#!/bin/bash\nDIR\u003d\"$(realpath -- \"${0%/*}\")\"\nexec vpython3 -vpython-spec \"${DIR}/run_tests.vpython3\" -m black \"$@\"\n```",
